{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"r0wj411y1iqdz8n8ecseh06","title":"Leftwm","desc":"","updated":1669736779009,"created":1669455858355,"custom":{},"fname":"linux.customization.leftwm","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"abde8e8d2e5014719db0a35ac675494c","links":[],"anchors":{"leftwm---ubuntu":{"type":"header","text":"LeftWM - ubuntu","value":"leftwm---ubuntu","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"install---ubuntu-install-from-source":{"type":"header","text":"Install - Ubuntu (install from source)","value":"install---ubuntu-install-from-source","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"config":{"type":"header","text":"Config","value":"config","line":36,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"0dcz8bz1ladgjebaljq61w7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"leftwm\">Leftwm<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#leftwm\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"leftwm---ubuntu\">LeftWM - ubuntu<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#leftwm---ubuntu\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leftwm.org/\">https://leftwm.org/</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/leftwm/leftwm\">https://github.com/leftwm/leftwm</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"install---ubuntu-install-from-source\">Install - Ubuntu (install from source)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install---ubuntu-install-from-source\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://rustup.rs/\">Install Rust &#x26; Cargo</a>\n<pre><code>curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>Get source code\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/leftwm/leftwm\n$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> leftwm\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>Build\n<pre><code>cargo build --profile optimized\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>Make leftwm executable\n<pre><code>sudo install -s -Dm755 ./target/release/leftwm ./target/release/leftwm-worker ./target/release/lefthk-worker ./target/release/leftwm-state ./target/release/leftwm-check ./target/release/leftwm-command -t /usr/bin\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>Create a desktop file\n<pre><code>sudo cp leftwm.desktop /usr/share/xsessions/\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"config\">Config<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#config\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/leftwm/leftwm#configuring\">https://github.com/leftwm/leftwm#configuring</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Install dependencies\n<ul>\n<li>picom</li>\n<li>polybar </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Themes: use current symlink</li>\n<li>Location: ~/.config/leftwm/config.ron</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](http